title: Magic of cinema returns for month-long festival (Belfast City Council)
text: ( Source : Belfast City Council ) 9 Oct 2015 The much anticipated Cinemagic film and television festival returns this weekend for a month long film feast, running from today (Friday 9 October) until 4 November , jam-packed with creative events
